---
---

<section class="relative min-h-[921px] flex items-center justify-center bg-surface overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      alt="Interior de la clinica VitaSmile"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center opacity-40 mix-blend-multiply"
      src="/fondoHero.png"
      loading="eager"
      decoding="async"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/80 via-white/50 to-white"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h1 data-animate style="transition-delay: 150ms" class="font-display-hero text-display-hero text-on-surface mb-stack-lg">
      Creamos tu confianza para sonreír
    </h1>
    <p data-animate style="transition-delay: 380ms" class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Recuperamos tu sonrisa y su salud con resultados naturales que perduren en el tiempo. Cada tratamiento está diseñado para ti, con la precisión y el cuidado que mereces.
    </p>
    <div data-animate style="transition-delay: 600ms" class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <button class="bg-primary hover:bg-surface-tint text-on-primary rounded-full px-8 py-4 font-body-md text-body-md shadow-[0_4px_14px_0_rgba(0,102,204,0.39)] transition-transform scale-95 active:scale-90">
        Agendar consulta
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
